10
1. Global Acquisition Strategy & Execution
· Build and execute performance marketing strategies across India, UK, Middle East, US, Africa & APAC
· Customize campaigns by region to match healthcare market maturity, personas, and platform trends
· Manage full-funnel acquisition for trials, demos, POCs, and paid conversions
 2. Multi-Region Paid Media Management
· Run paid campaigns across Google, LinkedIn, Meta, YouTube, programmatic platforms.
· Own regional budgets with clear CAC, CPL, CPA, and pipeline-generation targets
· Scale successful channels and test new ones across mature and emerging markets
· Build persona-specific targeting for clinicians, hospitals, CIOs, radiologists, and specialists
 3. CRM & Automation (Global Nurture)
· Build global nurture sequences for different funnels (inbound, outbound, partner-led)
· Optimize automation flows across HubSpot.
· Personalize messaging by geography and buyer persona
 4. Funnel, Attribution & Conversion Optimization
· Continuously improve landing pages for each region with A/B tests
· Optimize conversion rates from first click → MQL → SQL → demo → activation
· Use advanced attribution models (multi-touch, data-driven, first/last touch)
· Collaborate with global growth teams to improve funnel drop-offs
5. Creative Strategy for Global Markets
· Work with content, and design team to produce localized creatives
· Craft high-impact global ad copies, video briefs, banners & doctor-led content
· Test region-specific formats (e.g., UK LinkedIn-heavy vs. GCC Google-heavy vs. US YouTube-heavy)
6. Insights, Forecasting & Leadership Reporting
· Build weekly dashboards for CAC, LTV, channel performance, and market-level ROI
· Provide insights to leadership for expansion planning and GTM models
· Conduct deep-dive analyses on global cohorts and growth opportunities
